Precautions when using 1. If you experience redness, swelling, itching, or any abnormal symptoms after using the product, consult a specialist.
2. Avoid use on wounded areas.
3. Storage and Handling Instructions: a) Keep out of reach of children.
b) Store away from direct sunlight.
4. Do not use in areas subject to shaking.
5. If the product gets into your eyes, rinse immediately.
6. If you are sensitive or allergic to carmine, use with caution.
